### B0 대비 효과
- **D1**: BULL +3.44%pp / BEAR +0.52%pp / 최종자산 **+393K (+3.66%)**
- **D8**: BULL +4.37%pp / BEAR +0.94%pp / 최종자산 **+532K (+4.95%)**

