| V1 | EMA OR (OBV+ATR≤30) | 11,426,386 | +17.23% | -2.53% | 11.7% | 49% | 15 |
| C2 | EMA OR O3 OR V2 | 11,330,067 | +20.29% | -5.81% | 14.9% | 48% | 12 |
| C1 | EMA OR O3 OR V4 | 11,327,604 | +20.29% | -5.83% | 14.9% | 47% | 11 |
| C3 | EMA OR O3 OR V6 | 11,320,058 | +18.59% | -4.55% | 12.0% | 46% | 17 |
| V2 | EMA OR (OBV+ATR≤20) | 11,020,441 | +17.36% | -6.10% | 14.9% | 47% | 9 |
| V4 | EMA OR (V2+RSI>45) | 11,018,046 | +17.36% | -6.12% | 14.9% | 46% | 8 |
| V6 | EMA OR (V1+고점근접) | 11,010,706 | +15.70% | -4.84% | 12.8% | 46% | 14 |
| V7 | EMA OR (OBV3봉↑+ATR≤25) | 10,842,449 | +15.14% | -5.84% | 15.7%❌ | 49% | 10 |
